product.title: Olivia's Little World - Large DIY Doll House, Dreamland Mansion 3 Floor Wooden Doll House for Child Kids Toddler, 12 inch Dolls, Barbie Sized
product.categories_flat: All Departments > Toys & Games > Featured Categories > Preschool > Pre-Kindergarten Toys > Activity > Dolls & Dollhouses
product.description: Enter a home of luxury with Olivia's Little World's Dreamland Dollhouse Mansion! This Barbie-sized dollhouse features an interactive design with intricate details including a roof top terrace, spiral staircase, elevator and double door garage. 20 accessories include a lawn mower, BBQ grill, umbrella, hanging plant, pendant light, toilet, bathtub, treadmill, lounge chair and foot rest, dinning table, 2 chairs, couch, and bed with pillow. 2 reusable sticker sheets allow your little one to customize their home, and a back panel can be flipped between a craft studio or office space. This lavish dollhouse measures 45" long, 13" deep, and 49” tall and is ideal for 12” dolls including Barbie dolls. Five LR44 batteries included (2 for light effects in the floor lamp and 3 for sound effects for the toilet).

date.raw: Reviewed in the United States on July 21, 2023

top_reviews.title: Daughter loves it and the accessories are fun and thought out well
top_reviews.body: I got this for my 2 year old and she is having a blast playing with this dollhouse. I always wanted one as a kid and I have to say, that this is so much more modern than what I remember back then. For starters, my husband put it together. His feedback is that it was "easy" to build because it didn't require power tools. But it was also a tad difficult at times because you have to pretty much guess how some of the pieces go together. You have to use common sense as sometimes you need to swap certain pieces, and the picture in the listing helped him a lot (ex: while all pieces are labeled, you need to figure out 'front' and 'back'). The only part he had a hard time with were the panels that are meant to be swapped and should just slide out. One of ours is kind of permanent now based on how he had to install it. But it's cool that kids can change the room scenery a bit this way.  The entire dollhouse has a mix of wood and mdf type wood (if that's the right term). I don't know how long this will last but I definitely don't think it will be the kind of dollhouse I can pass down to grandkids, etc. It comes with several accessories, and most of them are made out of wood. Which I think is a pretty cool touch. The bed it came with was the only questionable one as it was pretty much dismantled and it was dirty (the cloth part of the bed cover). My favorite piece is a little lamp that actually lights up! My second favorite is the flushing toilet! Really cute and thoughtful pieces included.  My daughter is loving it and plays with all her little dolls. We don't have barbie dolls but some shorter ones and they work perfectly in this house. Definitely recommend this doll house. I'm so glad we got it for her (and for her little sister once she's older).Read more

date.raw: Reviewed in the United States on April 7, 2023

top_reviews.title: Darling, well made dollhouse
top_reviews.body: Dollhouse arrived in an enormous box, every piece well packed and in perfect condition. Took my handy husband about an hour to put together once everything was unpacked. The size is perfect for Barbies, and I've placed one of my daughters Barbies in the photos for reference. The house is made of wood, as are most of the accessories. The items that light up and make noise (toilet, lamp) are plastic. One complaint is that each piece of the house had a letter sticker on it for assembly. The stickers should have been on the back of the house pieces, because when pulled off, they pulled the darling background (see photo). So disappointing, and I took a star off for this.  The house isn't perfect, but much better quality than many things on the market today. Most importantly, my daughter spends hours playing with this thing. Recommended, though I would watch the price. Like many items on Amazon, I've seen this fluctuate pretty significantly.Read more

top_reviews.title: Love this dollhouse, but pricey
top_reviews.body: We really like this dollhouse, but I have to admit that it would take a little work to change up the style/decor in it since it’s mostly just printed on the walls.  The feature that I love the most about this dollhouse is that it fits full size Barbies and similar dolls. I imagine this doll house will last a long time.  My biggest complaint here is the price. While this is a large dollhouse, it isn’t very intricate like others I’ve seen that go for the same price. Like I mentioned before, most of it is printed on the walls and the outside or front of the house doesn’t have much to offer. If you plan to keep it up against a wall anyway, then it’s perfect.Read more

date.raw: Reviewed in the United States on January 31, 2023

top_reviews.title: Amazing dollhouse!
top_reviews.body: My wife's favorite toy growing up was her dollhouse, and ever since we had our daughter she's been dreaming of getting her a great dollhouse like the one she had. We got this one for her now that she's three and starting to do more imaginative play with dolls - she absolutely loves it!  The material is wood and feels high quality and sturdy, it's going to last her until she's too old for dolls anymore. A lot of the other dollhouses we've looked at are cheap plastic. It was easy to assemble, no more complicated than any of the other flat pack furniture we've assembled over the years. Someone mentioned peeling the assembly label stickers off would pull off the background of the wall pieces, so I took extra care with those. I used a scraper with a razor blade and they came right off without any damage.  It's huge, with four floors and big enough to be used with the Barbies I'm sure she'll get over the years. It came with a bunch of furniture which is awesome. Other dollhouses we've looked at make you buy furniture separate.  Overall a really great dollhouse that our daughter is going to enjoy for years!Read more
